    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Gameplay Loop:\n\tCollect Cards by Opening Packs or Wonder Pick.\n\nHow
    to Acquire Packs:\n\tYou can buy Packs in the Shop with the \n\tCurrency, Kromies.\n\nHow
    to Buy Cards:\n\tWhile Inspecting a Card, You can Buy that Card \n\twith the
    Currency, Cores. \n\nHow to Earn Cores:\n\tWhen Inspecting a Card, You can Shred
    the Card\n\tand Dissolve them into Cores.\n\nHow to Earn Kromies:\n\tYou earn
    1 Kromie every hour. This includes \n\tboth Online and Offline time.\n\nHow to
    Earn Loupes:\n\tYou earn 1 Loupe a day. They can be earned\n\tby completing different
    Tasks.\n\nViewing your Collection:\n\tIn the Collection screen, you can select
    and \n\tview a Pack's offerings, and see which you \n\town and dont. Owned Cards
    appear with full \n\tcolor, while Unowned Cards appear with no color.\n\nInspecting
    Cards:\n\tWhile in the Collection screen, you can right-click \n\ton a Card to
    view more information.\n\nOpening Packs:\n\tTo Open a Pack, left-click on one
    of the three \n\tPacks in the Main Menu. Next, Drag either Dot \n\tto its opposite
    side. Left-click on each Card to \n\tacknowledge it and move on to the next one.
    \n\tAfter the last Card, you will be returned to the \n\tMain Menu.\n\nWonder
    Pick:\n\tWonder Pick is the ability to select a card from 5\n\trandom cards from
    each card set. Each Wonder\n\tPick is able to be picked once a day. During a
    \n\tWonder Pick, you can use a Loupe, by \n\tright-clicking the card, to temporarily
    view the \n\tcard. To pick a card, left-click it.\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
