    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Task Types:\r\n\tThere are 3 different types of Tasks;\r\n\tMissions,
    Quests, and Challenges.\r\n\r\nMissions:\r\n\tMissions are daily Tasks. They
    can be completed\r\n\tonce each day and are refreshed daily.\r\n\r\nQuests:\r\n\tQuests
    are weekly Tasks. They can be completed\r\n\tonce each week and are refreshed
    weekly. \r\n\r\nChallenges:\r\n\tChallenges are account based Tasks. They can
    be\r\n\tcompleted only once per account.\r\n\r\nRewards:\r\n\tThe Rewards for
    each Task vary, and are given\r\n\timmediately upon Task completion.\r\n\r\nTask
    Progress:\r\n\tTo view progress of a certain Task, navigate to its\r\n\tspecific
    section under the Task Tab.\r\n\nReset:\n\tDaily Reset is at midnight, 00:00
    UTC. Weekly\n\tReset is every Monday at Daily Reset."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
